<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<xliff xmlns="urn:oasis:names:tc:xliff:document:1.2" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" version="1.2" xsi:schemaLocation="urn:oasis:names:tc:xliff:document:1.2 xliff-core-1.2-transitional.xsd">
  <file datatype="xml" source-language="en" target-language="ko" original="../AgentCommandStrings.resx">
    <body>
      <trans-unit id="ConfigUpdatesSelectPrompt">
        <source>The following agent configurations use the deprecated 'mcp start' command. Update them?</source>
        <target state="translated">다음 에이전트 구성에서 더 이상 사용되지 않는 'mcp start' 명령을 사용하고 있습니다. 업데이트하시겠습니까?</target>
        <note />
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="DeprecatedConfigFix">
        <source>Run 'aspire agent init' to update configuration</source>
        <target state="translated">구성을 업데이트하도록 'agent init' 명령 실행</target>
        <note />
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="DeprecatedConfigUpdate_Description">
        <source>Update {0} config to use new 'agent mcp' command</source>
        <target state="translated">새 'agent mcp' 명령을 사용하도록 {0} 구성 업데이트</target>
        <note />
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="DeprecatedConfigWarning">
        <source>{0} config uses deprecated 'mcp start' command</source>
        <target state="translated">{0} config에서 더 이상 사용되지 않는 'mcp start' 명령을 사용하고 있습니다.</target>
        <note />
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="Description">
        <source>Manage AI agent environment configuration</source>
        <target state="translated">AI 에이전트 환경 구성 관리</target>
        <note />
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="InitCommand_ConfigureMcpServer">
        <source>Install Aspire MCP server</source>
        <target state="translated">Andrew MCP 서버 설치</target>
        <note />
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="InitCommand_Description">
        <source>Initialize agent environment configuration for detected agents</source>
        <target state="translated">검색된 에이전트에 대한 에이전트 환경 구성 초기화</target>
        <note />
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="InitCommand_InstallSkillFile">
        <source>Install Aspire skill file (Recommended)</source>
        <target state="translated">스킬 파일 설치(권장)</target>
        <note />
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="InitCommand_NothingSelected">
        <source>No options selected. Nothing to configure.</source>
        <target state="translated">옵션을 선택하지 않았습니다. 구성할 항목이 없습니다.</target>
        <note />
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="InitCommand_WhatToConfigure">
        <source>What would you like to configure? [dim](Enter to skip, Ctrl+C to cancel)[/]</source>
        <target state="translated">무엇을 구성하시겠습니까? [dim](건너뛰려면 Enter, 취소하려면 Ctrl+C)[/]</target>
        <note />
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="MalformedConfigFileError">
        <source>The configuration file '{0}' contains malformed JSON. Please fix the file manually and re-run the command.</source>
        <target state="translated">구성 파일 '{0}'에 잘못된 형식의 JSON이 포함되어 있습니다. 파일을 직접 수정하고 명령을 다시 실행하세요.</target>
        <note />
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="McpCommand_Description">
        <source>Start the MCP (Model Context Protocol) server</source>
        <target state="translated">MCP(모델 컨텍스트 프로토콜) 서버 시작</target>
        <note />
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="SkipNoneDescription">
        <source>None — skip</source>
        <target state="translated">없음 – 건너뛰기</target>
        <note />
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="SkippedMalformedConfigFile">
        <source>Skipping update of '{0}'.</source>
        <target state="translated">'{0}'의 업데이트를 건너뛰는 중입니다.</target>
        <note />
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="ConfigurationCompletedWithErrors">
        <source>Configuration completed with errors. Please fix the reported issues and re-run the command.</source>
        <target state="translated">구성이 완료되었지만 오류가 발생했습니다. 보고된 문제를 해결하고 명령을 다시 실행하세요.</target>
        <note />
      </trans-unit>
    </body>
  </file>
</xliff>